{"tid":1418034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊間一芳真罷工?","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T08:56:24.000Z","uid":57555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5c796de2200dc829de64fac7bed6a9e031ca95b4","tid":1418034,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>作為某區一芳員工的朋友<br />\n我有必要出黎講下<br />\n今日我朋友返嗰間都冇開<br />\n佢哋(一芳員工)琴晚叫佢唔好開<br />\n佢(一芳老闆)一意孤行要開<br />\n直到今朝一個full time員工因為太危險返唔到去開鋪<br />\n佢先冇開<br />\n所以佢唔係自願罷工<br />\n係被罷工</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1416651/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1416651/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n其他POST巴打提過<br />\n太古、大埔、樂富、葵涌都冇開<br />\n求FC邊間係罷工，邊間係開唔到?<br />\n<br />\n罷工嘅都係同路人，特別係被人點名果間<br />\n一定要撐<br />\n唔係仲邊有鋪頭支持場運動同罷工?<br />\n<br />\n至於好似上面講果D開唔到<br />\n仲要扮罷工R支持<br />\n比開鋪果D更賤格<br />\n抵制係必需"},{"pid":"981b21870a849a422dac301b4c8672ad3f8668c5","tid":1418034,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/05/233228_c0333f46918ad81a8bd703889b3ca3cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F05%2F233228_c0333f46918ad81a8bd703889b3ca3cb.png&h=35b17368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有香港代理<br />\n呢篇聲明唔夠<br />\n一要同大陸奇割蓆<br />\n二屌番佢轉頭啦<br />\n你又唔係underder佢<br />\n啖有咩資格講解約?<br />\n莊閒都唔識分"},{"pid":"8f66eeaa60d4f9a532d883975aa16bceff622b7e","tid":1418034,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8hoxBeX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8hoxBeX.png&h=f00354bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銅鑼灣，沙田，大埔，樂富，太古，馬鞍山，葵涌，旺角<br />\n以上都唔係名單上<br />\n屬於冇開<br />\n求fc係咪罷工"},{"pid":"42fb7d6c91a331dda16ef74e7296b5e89cc8f088","tid":1418034,"uid":91343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f66eeaa60d4f9a532d883975aa16bceff622b7e","tid":1418034,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8hoxBeX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8hoxBeX.png&h=f00354bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銅鑼灣，沙田，大埔，樂富，太古，馬鞍山，葵涌，旺角<br />\n以上都唔係名單上<br />\n屬於冇開<br />\n求fc係咪罷工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"太古fc<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4U6bVau.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4U6bVau.jpg&h=1b6fbb14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好開心，見到太古城中心，香港有得救！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1413176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1413176</a>"},{"pid":"02265b90f393aeaae89a838a711e33cea32024c2","tid":1418034,"uid":245491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f66eeaa60d4f9a532d883975aa16bceff622b7e","tid":1418034,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8hoxBeX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8hoxBeX.png&h=f00354bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銅鑼灣，沙田，大埔，樂富，太古，馬鞍山，葵涌，旺角<br />\n以上都唔係名單上<br />\n屬於冇開<br />\n求fc係咪罷工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:03:50.000Z","msg":"仲有尖東"},{"pid":"b38447e2b99825f572511fa9b567b885f040cbf2","tid":1418034,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:51:52.000Z","msg":"一芳老闆絕對係企係我地呢邊 我以身份保證 唔好怪錯同路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418810</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />究竟係點"},{"pid":"966027969ec465e5599dd39862dc654934c4d987","tid":1418034,"uid":293897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b38447e2b99825f572511fa9b567b885f040cbf2","tid":1418034,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply